{"title":"上云初体验","uid":"689df84d2009e979bfd4b50e46006d81","slug":"上云初体验","date":"2022-03-26T01:34:51.000Z","updated":"2022-04-08T14:18:44.586Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/上云初体验.json","keywords":"Blog","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/network-2402637_1280.jpg"],"content":"<p>前情提要：之前一直白嫖[码云](<a href=\"https://gitee.com/murphyhou\">MurphyHou (murphyhou) - Gitee.com</a>)的仓库作为图床，然后一看，自己所有的图片都被换成了Gitee的logo，上网上查了一下，原来是码云屏蔽了仓库的外链。没办法，转战一个新的图床，Github和Gitee是一个性质的，免费，但也有可能被屏蔽外链，另外还有就是速度太慢了。那就直接消费一把，买云存储吧。</p>\n<p>这应该是第二次用阿里云了，第一次用的时候是使用了阿里云的容器镜像空间配置深度学习，<a href=\"https://cosmicdusty.cc/2021/11/21/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95/\">第一次深度学习尝试 - Murphy (cosmicdusty.cc)</a></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h1 id=\"阿里云SSO\"><a href=\"#阿里云SSO\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"阿里云SSO\"></a>阿里云SSO</h1><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">中文</th>\n<th align=\"center\">英文</th>\n<th align=\"center\">说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">存储空间</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Bucket</td>\n<td align=\"center\">存储空间是您用于存储对象（Object）的容器，所有的对象都必须隶属于某个存储空间。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">对象/文件</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Object</td>\n<td align=\"center\">对象是 OSS 存储数据的基本单元，也被称为OSS的文件。对象由元信息（Object Meta）、用户数据（Data）和文件名（Key）组成。对象由存储空间内部唯一的Key来标识。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">地域</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Region</td>\n<td align=\"center\">地域表示 OSS 的数据中心所在物理位置。您可以根据费用、请求来源等综合选择数据存储的地域。详情请查看<a href=\"https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/31837.htm#concept-zt4-cvy-5db\">OSS已经开通的Region</a>。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">访问域名</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Endpoint</td>\n<td align=\"center\">Endpoint 表示OSS对外服务的访问域名。OSS以HTTP RESTful API的形式对外提供服务，当访问不同地域的时候，需要不同的域名。通过内网和外网访问同一个地域所需要的域名也是不同的。具体的内容请参见<a href=\"https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/31837.htm#concept-zt4-cvy-5db\">各个Region对应的Endpoint</a>。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">访问密钥</td>\n<td align=\"center\">AccessKey</td>\n<td align=\"center\">AccessKey，简称 AK，指的是访问身份验证中用到的AccessKeyId 和AccessKeySecret。OSS通过使用AccessKeyId 和AccessKeySecret对称加密的方法来验证某个请求的发送者身份。AccessKeyId用于标识用户，AccessKeySecret是用户用于加密签名字符串和OSS用来验证签名字符串的密钥，其中AccessKeySecret 必须保密。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"购买配置\"><a href=\"#购买配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"购买配置\"></a>购买配置</h2><p>购买和配置过程比较简单，也我当时也没记录，网上的教程很多，放几个参考教程的链接吧。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.aliyun.com/article/787128\">使用阿里云对象存储OSS+PicGo搭建图床-阿里云开发者社区 (aliyun.com)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/104152479\">阿里云OSS PicGo 配置图床教程 超详细 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/fengxiandada/article/details/123747655\">gitee图床用不了，阿里云OSS搭建图床(非常详细)_每天都要加油呀！的博客-CSDN博客</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"SSO防盗链\"><a href=\"#SSO防盗链\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SSO防盗链\"></a>SSO防盗链</h2><div align=center>\n    <img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220327092239189.png\"/>\n</div>\n\n<h1 id=\"购买域名\"><a href=\"#购买域名\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"购买域名\"></a>购买域名</h1><p>从网站最开始的时候只有一个index界面，到套用网页模板，再到现在的时候hexo部署网站，网站已经经历了三次大的变化了。域名也改过两次了，现在的域名太长了，我就想买个域名玩一下。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markdown\" data-language=\"markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">2020.12：https://murphyhou0928.github.io/  GitHub改名了，这个访问不了了\n2022.01：https://murphyhoucn.github.io/   其实现在还在用这个，只不过是会自己链接到cosmicdusty.cc\n2022.03：https://cosmicdusty.cc/<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>参考教程：<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/e258a46df9b7\">GitHub搭建博客自定义域名 - 简书 (jianshu.com)</a></p>\n<p>几个踩坑的地方。</p>\n<p>大部分教程都是设置的记录类型为“A”，记录值为ping<a href=\"https://username.github.io/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%97%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84IPV4%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AFGithub%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%88%91%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%90CNAME%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A\">https://username.github.io/博客网站时显示的IPV4地址，我一开始也是这样设置的，但是Github会给一个警告，要求我设置成CNAME类型的域名解析。如下：</a></p>\n<div align=center>\n    <img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220327093537272.png\"/>\n</div>\n\n<p>使用Hexo部署网站的时候会出现部署后域名就不能访问了，这时候要在本地建CNAME文件,然后再hexo d。注意目录结构！</p>\n<div align=center>\n    <img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220327094142180.png\"/>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"感受\"><a href=\"#感受\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"感受\"></a>感受</h1><p>云服务近几年发展的越来越好了，厂商提供的功能也越来越多，体验也不错，另外价格不算贵。未来肯定会接触到越来越多的云体验，所以学会使用云服务还是很重要的。这次只是使用了云存储，希望下一次能用一下云服务器，之前深度学习算是第一次使用。<a href=\"https://cosmicdusty.cc/2021/11/21/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95/\">第一次深度学习尝试 - Murphy (cosmicdusty.cc)</a></p>\n<p>云服务的设置太多了，需要不断学习，不断使用。</p>\n","feature":false,"text":"前情提要：之前一直白嫖[码云](MurphyHou (mur...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.8k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"知识扩展","slug":"知识扩展","count":10,"path":"api/categories/知识扩展.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"云存储","slug":"云存储","count":1,"path":"api/tags/云存储.json"},{"name":"域名","slug":"域名","count":1,"path":"api/tags/域名.json"},{"name":"GitHub","slug":"GitHub","count":4,"path":"api/tags/GitHub.json"},{"name":"云服务","slug":"云服务","count":2,"path":"api/tags/云服务.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91SSO\"><span class=\"toc-text\">阿里云SSO</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">购买配置</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#SSO%E9%98%B2%E7%9B%97%E9%93%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">SSO防盗链</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">购买域名</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">感受</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/18627097/murphy","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"半导体厂商","uid":"ff5739d0da8d45c28672b5fbc56cf20c","slug":"半导体厂商","date":"2022-03-28T09:15:21.000Z","updated":"2022-04-08T14:28:14.943Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/半导体厂商.json","keywords":"Blog","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/board-22098_1920.jpg"],"text":"汇总常见的半导体厂商的概况以及他们的兴衰。 半导体厂商之间的...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"15k","symbolsTime":"13 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"电子电路","slug":"电子电路","count":5,"path":"api/categories/电子电路.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"半导体","slug":"半导体","count":2,"path":"api/tags/半导体.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/18627097/murphy","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},"next_post":{"title":"整理Wi